mpic history.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998730172673, \"rank\": 1.2698292772919943e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Previous gold medal winners\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Callaghan\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"Ronnie DelaneyandKatie Taylorhave\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the annals\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ireland's first Olympic medal wasn't for athletics or boxing.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998730172673, \"rank\": 1.2698292772919943e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was instead awarded for a painting byJack B. Yeats.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a painting\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"B. Yeats\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won silver for his workThe Liffey Swimand the first ever Olympic medal for Ireland as an independent nation.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1032, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998730172673, \"rank\": 1.2698292772919943e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\